# 1) High-Level Objective

Ensure tools read settings via `config/loader.py` (e.g., `get_config_value`) rather than inline dict access or hardcoded defaults.

# 2) Steps

1. Identify inline config access sites (e.g., LLM defaults in agents).
2. Replace with loader accessors; define defaults centrally.

# 3) Acceptance Criteria

- All config reads use loader; defaults live in settings.yaml or loader.
